影，如《[[微软太空模拟器|微软太空模拟器]]》<ref name="space_sim_1994">{{cite web | first = Lee | last = Buchanan | title = The Final Frontier | url = http://www.planetmic.com/mlahren/spasim6.htm | publisher = PC Gamer | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200807102328/http://www.planetmic.com/mlahren/spasim6.htm | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-08-18 | date = 1994-11 | archivedate = 2020-08-07}}</ref>、《[[轨道器_(模拟器)|轨道器]]》<ref name="OrbiterReview">{{cite web | last = Irving | first = Bruce | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191031183408/http://thespacereview.com/article/494/1 | archivedate = 2019-10-31 | url = https://www.thespacereview.com/article/494/1 | title = Review: Orbiter space flight simulator | publisher = The Space Review | date = 2005-11-14 | accessdate = 2020-08-18}}</ref>和《[[航天飞机任务2007|航天飞机任务2007]]》<ref name="shuttle_2007">{{cite web | title = Space Shuttle Mission Simulation | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200807102646/https://www.space-shuttle-mission.com/about.html | deadurl = no | publisher = Simsquared Ltd. | date = 2007 | url = https://www.space-shuttle-mission.com/about.html | accessdate = 2020-08-18 | archivedate = 2020-08-07}}</ref>。[[美国邮政署|美国邮政署]]已发行多种描绘航天飞机的邮票，其中首枚于1981年面世，现在[[国家邮政博物馆|国家邮政博物馆]]展出<ref name="stamps">{{cite web | title = 18c Columbia Space Shuttle single | work = Space Achievement Issue | publisher = Arago | date = 2020 | url = https://www.si.edu/es/object/npm_1994.2027.412?width=85%25&height=85%25&iframe=true&destination=spotlight/music-stamps | accessdate = 2020-08-18 | archive-date = 2020-08-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200819155505/https://www.si.edu/es/object/npm_1994.2027.412?width=85%25&height=85%25&iframe=true&destination=spotlight%2Fmusic-stamps | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

